videos.description: Jared Harper steals an inbound pass and takes it to the hole for Auburn.
videos.headline: Tight defense leads to Harper layup

videos.description: Jared Harper connects with a cutting Mustapha Heron, who takes the pass and throws down dunk.
videos.headline: Auburn's Heron goes backdoor for slam

videos.description: The Tigers bounce back from a one-point loss to Texas A&M with a convincing 78-61 win over Georgia.
videos.headline: Auburn takes battle against Georgia
